flowchart TD
    A([Start: Report Suite Strategy]) --> B{Single brand?}
    B -- Yes --> C{Single region?}
    B -- No --> D[Multi-suite with shared base configuration]
    C -- Yes --> E[Global suite — one report suite, virtual report suites for segments]
    C -- No --> F{Data residency or compliance requirement per region?}
    F -- Yes --> G[Regional report suites — data stays in-region]
    F -- No --> E
    D --> H{Need unified cross-brand attribution?}
    H -- Yes --> I[Add CJA on top of global suite]
    H -- No --> D
    E --> J{Need cross-channel attribution beyond web?}
    J -- Yes --> I
    J -- No --> K[Analysis Workspace — done]
    I --> L[Customer Journey Analytics — done]
    G --> M[Consider CJA for cross-region rollup]
